def my_func(input1: int):
    if not (1 <= input1 <= 10000):
        return None
    
    quarters = input1 // 25
    remaining_cents = input1 % 25
    
    dimes = remaining_cents // 10
    remaining_cents %= 10
    
    nickels = remaining_cents // 5
    pennies = remaining_cents % 5
    
    return quarters, dimes, nickels, pennies
